{
  "texts": [
    "Utilizing AI, distance, time, space, access to current learning materials, travel costs, and travel risks are no longer significant barriers.",
    "Rapid technological advancement indicates that AI e-learning will inevitably elevate the standard of higher education [62].",
    "Regarding the downsides, AI technologies come at a considerable cost, which not every nation can afford [63].",
    "Additionally, applying AI in a system can present numerous difficulties [64].",
    "Angib et al. [64] argues that before delving into artificial intelligence, obstacles such as insufficient financial resources, waning interest among institutional administrations, a lack of knowledge regarding successful engagements in the field, and a scarcity of studies addressing pertinent assertions must be carefully considered and effectively addressed.Considering the paramount importance of advancing technological solutions in education, Nigeria currently lags in embracing such innovations."
  ]
}